Job Board

Stack: React Native, React, JavaScript, ExpoGo

Fullstack Job Search application made in React Native. The application fetches APIs, follows correct system architecture and implements search and pagination functionality.

Inspire My Space

Stack: React, Three.js, JavaScript, Python, Flask, Pytest, Vite, CSS, Render, Github, Amazon S3, Docker, PostgreSQL

A website that harnesses the capabilities of 3D rendering technologies to enable spaces to be represented in their truest and most authentic form, eliminating the risks of misinterpretation and deceptive visuals. The platform allows designers, estate agents and airbnb hosts to create fully-3d rendered virtual environments of design concepts and properties.

Roboto Artworks

Stack: Figma, JavaScript, P5.js, Node.js, TouchDesigner, CSS, HTML

Introducing Roboto Artworks, a contemporary artist showing works from scuplture to digital design. This website harnesses p5.js to enable interactivity of moving around a constellation with mousemovement.

Studio4

Stack: Adobe Muse, JavaScript, P5.js, Node.js, TouchDesigner, CSS, HTML

Studio4 specalise in new media formats and the future of Video and Audio Podcast. The technologies used harnesses steering behaviours and physics to create an interactive platform.

Florin County Council

Stack: HTML, JavaScript, SQL, Node.js, Jest, Vite, CSS, Render

A place to increase community involvement and showcase what Florin has to offer. Fullstack application that uses RESTful apis, encrypted sign up system and has a 70% test coverage with JEST.
